<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>MediaLab Support</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png" type="image/png" />
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-slate-100">
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 sm:py-16">
      <a href="/" class="text-cyan-300 text-sm font-bold">Back to MediaLab</a>
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight">Support</h1>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-slate-300 leading-7">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Need help?</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">Use the in-app feedback flow for product issues, payout questions, or hosting problems. Include the project name, provider involved, and a short description of what went wrong.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Fastest way to resolve issues</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">For GitHub or Render setup issues, send the project name and deployment URL. For AdSense issues, include the exact live URL and current status shown in your Console.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
